dct_title_s: The countries of the Caribbean : including Mexico, Central America, the West Indies and the Panama Canal
dct_alternative_sm: The countries of the Caribbean : including Mexico, Central America, the West Indies and the Panama Canal
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by bathymetry, spot heights and gradient tints.; Shows steamship routes and U.S. consular offices and agencies.; Insets: Guantanamo Bay, Cuba; approximately 1:400,000.--Porto Rico and the Virgin Islands; approximately 1:1,300,000.--The Panama Canal and the Canal Zone (with cross-section showing extent of canal excavation); approximately 1:500,000.
